AI Image Generation Prompt
A serene traditional Japanese landscape illustration in the style of classic ukiyo-e and watercolor wash painting.
Foreground features a calm reflective lake with smooth stone formations and delicate cherry blossom trees in full bloom, their petals softly touching the water’s surface. Midground shows an elegant arched wooden bridge spanning the lake, leading the eye toward two traditional pagodas partially hidden among pink and white sakura trees. Background reveals a majestic Mount Fuji rising gently through light mist, centered and symmetrical, enhancing balance and harmony. A small flock of birds flies across the pale sky, adding motion and depth.
Style & Medium:
Traditional Japanese ukiyo-e meets soft watercolor illustration, hand-painted texture, subtle paper grain, ink-wash outlines, refined brushwork, painterly softness.
Composition:
Wide landscape view, balanced symmetry, layered depth (foreground rocks → bridge → pagodas → mountain), natural framing with overhanging cherry branches, strong horizontal flow.
Atmosphere & Mood:
Tranquil, meditative, poetic, springtime serenity, timeless and dreamlike.
Color Palette:
Soft pastels and muted earth tones — blush pinks, warm coral, ivory whites, sage green, muted teal, warm wood browns, cool gray-blue mountain hues.
Lighting:
Diffuse natural daylight, overcast spring light, gentle highlights, no harsh shadows.
Camera / Perspective (if applicable):
Wide-angle landscape view, eye-level perspective, deep focus, no lens distortion.
Details & Enhancements:
Mirror-like water reflections, drifting petals, light mist, minimal contrast, high detail, ultra-clean composition, no modern elements, no text, no people.
Aspect Ratio:
3:2 or 16:9
Quality:
Ultra-high resolution, fine art illustration, cinematic calm, museum-quality print aesthetic.
